Building Predator on Ubuntu
===========================
Note I do not use Ubuntu myself, so this howto may become outdated as time pass
by.  Any suggestions from real Ubuntu users on how to improve this howto are
welcome.  Please replace XXXXXX by the latest release of Predator (for example
predator-2011-07-07-216f2b8).

    sudo apt-get install cmake curl         \
        libgmp3-dev libmpc-dev libmpfr-dev  \
        gcc-multilib

    curl http://www.fit.vutbr.cz/~idudka/download/XXXXXX.tar.gz
        | gzip -cd \
        | tar x

    cd XXXXXX

    make -j3 build_boost build_gcc

    make -j3

    make check
